Exception\\r\\n    + FullyQualifiedErrorId : CommandNotFoundException\\r\\n \\r\\n\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"finish_reason\": \"tool-calls\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"total_tokens\": 76461,\n        \"context_window\": 200000\n      },\n      \"source\": \"api\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"nextCursor\": \"umsg_433857ee948a47b1b5a14986258065fb\"\n}\n",
